Package: ConfMatrix
Type: Package
Title: Confusion Matrix
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Paola Barba Ceballos
Maintainer: Paola Barba Ceballos <pbarba@ujaen.es>
Description: This package is made using object-oriented programming, it provides several indices applicable to the confusion matrix to obtain information on the quality of the classification carried out. In addition, quality control of the classification can be carried out taking into account the reference data. It contains the 'ConfMatrix' and 'QCCS' classes created with R6.
Imports: R6, Rdpack, ggplot2, gridExtra
RdMacros: Rdpack
License: GPL
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
VignetteBuilder: knitr
